title: Tim and Eric's Bedtime Stories: "Toes" S1E02
description:
Tim & Eric's Bedtime Stories, episode 2: "Toes"
The title of this episode and the last episode both say episode 2 but this is the real one. As someone pointed out, the last episode was really episode 1 and the Haunted House episode was the pilot. The stuttering isn't so bad in this episode but the quality still isn't HD unfortunately. Enjoy Bob Odenkirk's greatness.
